{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"7c5540d2-9efd-4658-83b7-355fe5a8e433","content":"Good news — in .NET 10, `dotnet test` **natively supports MTP**. The `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport` property was a .NET 9 bridge and is **no longer needed**. The new `dotnet test` automatically detects MTP-enabled projects.\n\nYou only need `EnableMSTestRunner` (which you already have). I'll clean up your csproj:","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_011ATKPdFGhqv9jznJZZpJse","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Removing obsolete MTP property"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01MhcAMF7z1wAdiAYNXgowKs","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-60a234efbae447a6a2a20a01c071d084/TestProject.csproj","old_str":"    <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>\n    <TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>true</TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>","new_str":"    <EnableMSTestRunner>true</EnableMSTestRunner>"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"edit the file at /tmp/sv-60a234efbae447a6a2a20a01c071d084/TestProject.csproj."}],"interactionId":"9888bb82-fb22-4078-aaf2-672bb4d95b23","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is on .NET 10 SDK (10.0.100) and wants to know about native MTP support. Let me check the latest information about .NET 10 and Microsoft.Testing.Platform.\n\nIn .NET 10, `dotnet test` has native support for Microsoft.Testing.Platform (MTP). The key change is:\n\n1. In .NET 10, `dotnet test` uses MTP natively as the default test runner when the test project is an MTP project (i.e., has `EnableMSTestRunner=true` or equivalent).\n2. The `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport` property is **no longer needed** in .NET 10. It was a bridge property introduced in .NET 9 to opt into the MTP-based `dotnet test` experience. In .NET 10, this is the default behavior.\n\n\n3. The user should remove `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport` from their project file since it's redundant, but keep `EnableMSTestRunner=true` to ensure the test project is recognized as an MTP project.","outputTokens":768,"requestId":"5C37:3CEFF5:B81EC:E6A74:69F54B6B"},"id":"1b2742b4-add8-4691-9242-bad60776065b","timestamp":"2026-05-02T00:55:48.197Z","parentId":"ef55daab-ab97-46ce-ae39-8156b9b92aa7"}
